Complete overcast- calm so far- several areas with high organic content on bottom/have unusual amount of weeds.

Breeze- very small waves- hazy and hot.

Partly cloudy- mild wind and waves.

Partly sunny- brisk west wind.  Trace rain 7/12 + 7/13.
